oto-Instagram-jariatudanita.png 750w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> LBD and a coat For an edgy look, pair your LBD with a slightly oversized coat/jacket. This look is not only comfortable but stylish and perfect for a cool environment. You can style this look with sneakers or heels for a girly-feel or even thigh-high boots.